==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unnun
<hw>Un*nun"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>nun</ets>.]</ety> <def>To remove from condition of
being a nun.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Many did quickly <qex>unnun</qex> and disfriar themselves.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unobedience</ent>⟦br⟧
